DESCRIPTION:Join us on Tuesday\, May 19\, from 4 - 7 PM at Whispering Vine - Fourth St. for a tasting featuring Schramsberg and special guest Laurant Sarazin\, Vice President of Sales.\nTasting Fee: $25 per person (Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.)\nFeatured Wines:\n- Schramsberg Blanc de Blancs 2022 – $35.99\, Winery $44 – Dynamic and fragrant\, offering lemon blossom\, orange peel and blanched almond flavors. Finishes on a vibrant\, fresh accent.\n- Schramsberg Blanc de Noirs 2022 – $39.99\, Winery $46 – Lively and refined but festive\, with pretty accents of strawberry\, lemon\, apple and graham cracker that sail on the crisp yet supple finish.\n- Schramsberg Brut Rose 2021 – $42.99\, Winery $50 – A lovely blush that's refined and festive\, with vibrant strawberry\, orange blossom and cherry flavors that glide on the refreshing finish.\nCome explore Schramsberg and find your favorite bottle. Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded.
LOCATION:4201 W Fourth St Reno\, NV 89523
SUMMARY:Schramsberg Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR